          "{Accuracy: 0.97 - Naive Bayes-PBC, F1-Score: 0.98 - Naive Bayes-PBC, Cohen’s Kappa: 0.94 - Naive Bayes-PBC}",
          "Authors present a framework of different learning behaviours call PBMC.\n\nThe work takes 12 learning behaviorsfrom one course and uses them build feature aggregations. Authors compare this representation against representations created by previous authors in the literature.\n\nAuthors show that their representation is better when compared against that of other algorithms…",
